title: What is new in SharePoint 2016
eventShortDescription:
In this session Adam Cogan will provide information about what is new in SharePoint 2016 and his personal favourites. The SharePoint Team has invested in many including:

  • UX support for Ajax
  • Their Web Content Management System
  • Digital Asset Management System (for videos)
  • Visual Studio 2015 tools for SharePoint 2016
  • Developer Platform
  • Office 2016 integration
  • RESTful Web API
  • Tagging and Rating
Lets see what is good and what is not.​​
